This is a Movie Website project built with React.js and Node.js.

Project Structure:
/frontend - Contains React.js frontend code
/backend - Contains Node.js backend code
/database - Contains database schemas and migrations

Development Guidelines:
- Use ES6+ features
- Follow React best practices
- Use camelCase for variables and functions
- Use PascalCase for component names
- Write clean, maintainable code with proper comments

The website allows users to:
- Browse movies
- Search for movies
- View movie details
- Rate and review movies
- Create user accounts
- Save favorite movies

Please help maintain consistent code style and suggest improvements when possible.